14.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Pomegranate-Martini.-1-3.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1731074675479\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is in a pomegranate martini? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe ingredients in a pomegranate martini are pomegranate juice, vodka, orange liqueur and fresh lemon juice. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1731074703167\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eHow to make a pomegranate martini? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eBegin by adding pomegranate juice, vodka, orange liqueur and lemon juice to a cocktail shaker half filled with ice. Shake for 10-15 seconds until well chilled. Strain and pour into a martini glass (bonus points for using a chilled glass). Garnish with a lemon twist or a sprig of fresh rosemary.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/pomegranate-martini/?tp_image_id=134049\" data-pin-title=\"Pomegranate Martini Recipe\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/P